// Primer SkeletonBox — upstream: primer-ui-react **`SkeletonBox.tsx`** + **`SkeletonBox.module.css`**
// (**`skeletonLoader-bgColor`**, **`borderRadius-small`**, shimmer **`var(--base-duration-1000)`**).
// Shimmer approximates **`mask-image`** (alpha **1 → 0.65**) over the fill: base layer at **`bgColor × 0.65`**, moving **`75deg`** gradient layer at **`bgColor × 0.35 → 0`** (same stops as CSS mask). Coverage **`×4`** width, **`x = -3 × width × phase`**. See **`SKELETON_BOX_CSS_REFERENCE.md`** / **`probe/README.md`**. **`reduce-motion`**: solid **`SkeletonTokens.bgColor`** only.

import { Palette } from "std-widgets.slint";
import { LayoutTokens, SkeletonTokens } from "../tokens.slint";

